bq. {color:red}'Array'{color} is less than 7 characters long</p>

<p>The PHP-Code:
{quote}$captcha = new Zend_Form_Element_Captcha(
    'captcha',
    array(
        'label' =&gt; 'Label',
        'captcha' =&gt; array(
            'captcha'         =&gt; 'Image',
            'wordLen'         =&gt; 7,
        ),
        'filters'    =&gt; array('StringTrim'),
        'validators' =&gt; array(
            array('NotEmpty', true),
            array('StringLength', true, array(7, 7))
        ),
        'required'   =&gt; true
    )
);{quote}</p>

